// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0269 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 369a8fdb-7faa-5ffe-a256-3ba10a6bce5a

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
